description: Alexa shows off her beat-boxing skills. Get a list of available beats by saying, "Yo! Yo! Yo!" (Right now, she knows 24 different beats.)  You can ask for a beat by name ("phat", "old school", "electronic", etc.) or "random".
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Beat Cylinder for Techno
